@startuml

title AZ Kviz - Vrstvy reseni a jejich spoluprace
top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Ucitel/Admin" as admin
actor "Hrac/Trida" as player

rectangle "Admin FE\n(admin.html + auth.js + api.js)" as admin_fe
rectangle "Herni FE\n(play.html + play.js + game.js)" as game_fe

rectangle "Google Identity Services\n(OAuth + ID token)" as gis
rectangle "Google OAuth tokeninfo" as tokeninfo

rectangle "Google Apps Script Web App\n(doGet/doPost)" as gas
rectangle "Auth guard\nverifyIdToken + isAllowed" as auth_guard

database "Google Sheets\n(quizzes, questions)" as sheets

admin --> admin_fe : ovladani admin UI
player --> game_fe : ovladani herni UI

admin_fe --> gis : Google Sign-In
gis --> admin_fe : ID token (JWT)

admin_fe --> gas : HTTPS GET/POST\naction + idToken + payload
game_fe --> gas : HTTPS GET\naction=getQuizForPlay&id

gas --> auth_guard : kontrola admin akci
auth_guard --> tokeninfo : overeni idToken
tokeninfo --> auth_guard : aud + email
auth_guard --> gas : allow/deny

gas --> sheets : read/write kvizu a otazek
sheets --> gas : data

note bottom of gas
Admin akce: listQuizzes/getQuiz/saveQuiz/deleteQuiz
vyzaduji validni idToken a email v ALLOWED_EMAILS.
getQuizForPlay je verejny endpoint pro herni FE.
end note

@enduml
